{"tid":192551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗牛牛一家四口馬路穿梭　警持盾牌戒備","createTime":"2017-04-08T16:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T16:02:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0511a6d1c242c1d6d72785c63a3cc697b46bcdb7","tid":192551,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>元朗牛牛一家四口馬路穿梭　警持盾牌戒備<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170408/bkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2Fbkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001.html&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9b2cbbb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170408/bkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001.html</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170408/photo/bkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170408183018\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170408183018&h=4794b353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有警員手持盾牌戒備。  (文健雄攝)</div><br />\n<br />\n流浪牛不只在郊區才看到，更會走入市區甚至衝出馬路！有網民今日下午在元朗發現牛牛一家四口，沒有遵守交通規則，牠們旁若無人，走入塞滿車輛的馬路上，如行cat walk，相當危險，不少網民也大感嘩然，指是第一次看見，亦有人稱在元朗看見流浪牛，一點也不出奇。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170408/photo/bkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001_04b.jpg?20170408183018\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20170408183018&h=43531d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4隻牛施施然在馬路中間行走。(「盡在元朗」fb」)</div><br />\n<br />\n下午5時許，警方接報到元朗公路過博愛醫院迴旋處往上水方向，多輛警車將4牛圍在路邊，有警員手持盾牌戒備，漁農自然護理署人員亦已到場，正等候獸醫前來協助。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170408/photo/bkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170408183018\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170408170152186-0408_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170408183018&h=f36e4fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多輛警車將牛隻圍在路邊。  (文健雄攝)</div><br />\n<br />\n有網民在「盡在元朗」facebook專頁上載多張圖片，相中所見，在繁忙的馬路上，4隻流浪牛有大有細，施施然在馬路中間行走，絲毫不擔心安全問題，看起來相當「牙煙」，亦引起不少網民迴響，指流浪牛原先在由元朗市中心出現，之後行到元朗YOHO MIDTOWN。有網民表示，「一家四牛在YOHO MIDTOWN對出的馬路上，駕駛者請小心。」另有網民表示，「琴(昨)日呢4隻係識行行人路口。」亦有稱是「牛牛出城啦！」"}]}